    {
        "content": "<p>I assumed <code>[complete_space ùïú]</code></p>",
        "id": 276963005,
        "sender_full_name": "Heather Macbeth",
        "timestamp": 1648535481
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>But indeed, the trace should be a bounded linear map without that assumption.</p>",
        "id": 276963101,
