        "timestamp": 1648536695
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Then you should be good to go with making</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">matrix.trace</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">fin</span> <span class=\"n\">n</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">ùïú</span> <span class=\"bp\">ùïú</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">‚àò‚Çó</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">algebra.lmul_left</span> <span class=\"bp\">ùïú</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">adjugate</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span><span class=\"o\">))</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>a \"native\" continuous linear map.</p>",
